data.description: Immediate Occupancy is available for this immaculate 3/2 town home with a 2-car garage. Enjoy carefree Florida living, with lawn maintenance and exterior paint included in the HOA. The home features high ceilings, plantation shutters, inside laundry, and brand-new A/C being installed before closing. Relax on the spacious patio while watching the wildlife graze. Halifax Plantation is convenient to I-95 and just 5 miles to beautiful Flagler Beach. Halifax Plantation offers dining, and memberships for pool, tennis, fitness, and golf. Schedule your tour today! All information taken from the tax record, and while deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed.
